Who is Southeast Asset Advisors, Inc. (SEA)? 
SEA is a non-commission, fee only, registered investment advisory firm, whose principals (See "Our Team") have been providing investment management services for more than 20 years, and using the same strategy to successfully achieve their personal investment goals. 
The mission for SEA's team is to provide sophisticated, objective investment advisory services on a fee only basis (no commissions), only after properly educating and consulting with our clients as to their goals, time horizon and risk tolerance, so that we can together design an asset allocation investment plan that will reach their goals with risks compatible with their determined financial profile. read more



