7, Bizjournals.com published: "CSX second quarter earnings exceed expectations" on July 18, 2017. The stock was purchased at an average cost of $51.59 per share, for a total transaction of $70,007,630.00. Following the transaction, the director now directly owns 106 shares in the company, valued at $5,468.54. The transaction was disclosed in a document filed with the Securities & Exchange Commission, which is available at the SEC website.








