About
Who is Southeast Asset Advisors, Inc. (SEA)?
SEA is a non-commission, fee only, registered investment advisory firm, whose principals (See “Our Team”) have been providing investment management services for more than 20 years, and using the same strategy to successfully achieve their personal investment goals. The mission for SEA’s team is to provide sophisticated, objective investment advisory services on a fee only basis (no commissions), only after properly educating and consulting with our clients as to their goals, time horizon and risk tolerance, so that we can together design an asset allocation investment plan that will reach their goals with risks compatible with their determined financial profile.
OUR INVESTMENT BELIEFS…
The following outlines, the investment philosophy we have developed over the last twenty-six years and has proven appropriate for our clients.
Investment Beliefs and Process
Pledge and Commitment to Our Clients

 
 


 
 
 

 



 
 
 
 




 “We assess the probability of correctly timing the market to be less than 1 in 6.  Successful timing of the market requires being right in three sequential events.”   
– Longleaf Partners–2nd Quarter Report, 1998

 
 
 
 




Pledge and Commitment to Our Clients

We are fee only advisors and represent only our clients! The only fee we charge our clients is based on percentage of assets under management.  We will not impair our independence by accepting any other form of compensation such as commissions, soft dollar deals, etc.  We will strive to be the lowest cost while being the highest quality financial quarterback for our clients.

 

We will strive to help design and update as necessary an asset allocation plan to meet a client’s established goals that will become a part of each client’s investment policy based on a thorough understanding of each client’s:



–  Goals & Objectives
–  Time Horizons
–  Income Needs
–  Risk Tolerance
–  Total Net Worth and Asset Pool under Management
